  case $(menu "Use default config" "´ıÖ  Hyprland\n´ıÖ  Hypridle\n´ıÖ  Hyprlock\n´ıÖ  Hyprsunset\n¾▒ú┤  Plymouth\n´ıØ  Swayosd\n¾░îğ  Walker\n¾░ı£  Waybar") in
